I have developed a simple and interactive To-Do List Web Application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project helps users to efficiently manage their daily tasks by allowing them to add, delete tasks in real time with a clean and user-friendly interface.

The application is designed with responsive styling using CSS and dynamic functionality using JavaScript, ensuring smooth performance and ease of use. It helps improve productivity by keeping tasks organized and easy to access.

